  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NetworkException
    This exception is thrown whenever the result of an operation is unknown due to a network error
    OutOfSpaceException
    This exception is thrown whenever there is no space to complete the requested operation.
    OverwriteException
    This exception is thrown whenever a write is attempted on a page that already has been written to.
    TrimmedException
    This exception is thrown whenever a read or write is attempted on a trimmed region.
    UnwrittenException
    This exception is thrown whenever a read is attempted on an unwritten page.
